<title type="html"><![CDATA[10/30( Sat)How to do digital detox/ Table topics session.(Host: Lawrence )]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=554&amp;p=577#p577"><![CDATA[
There is no on-site meeting during the pandemic of COVID-19.<br /><br />加入 Zoom 會議<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... NKSU5MQT09<br /><br />會議 ID：929 8726 6213<br />密碼：112233<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:10-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Presentation 1<br />8:00-8:10 pm Break<br />8:10-8:40: Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation 2<br /><br />At the presentation, the time limit is 1-2 minutes for each speaker.<br />Session 1 doing detox<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.verywellmind.com/why-and-how-to-do-a-digital-detox-4771321">https://www.verywellmind.com/why-and-ho ... ox-4771321</a><!-- m --> <br />Questions for discussion<br />1. Do you think digital detoxing is necessary? Are you suffering from digital toxin?<br />2. What kind of digital toxin do you want to avoid?<br />3. What do you think of technology and cell phone?<br />4. What do you think is the most benefit you get from Internet and the harm hard to shake off?<br />5. Do you spend too much time on cell phone or Internet?<br /><br /><br />Session 2 ‘impromptu discussion + impromptu speech’ <br />For impromptu discussion time (40 minutes), each person prepares one or two questions for his group discussion.<br />For impromptu speech time ( 20 minutes), the host will prepare some questions to ask. (assign someone to answer or may ask a volunteer’. The purpose of impromptu speech (Table topic) is to train the speaker to give a speech without any preparation. <br />Speaking time will be strictly controlled. Each answer is for 2 minutes.<br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=89">AndrewWang</a> — Mon Oct 25, 2021 11:06 pm</p><hr />
